              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/24143286/" class="">第113页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/49710898/" class=" " title="matsu770610">matsu770610</a>
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="24143286">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">编辑校对还是不力啊
这一页就有两处错误
【大义】里面“天在地上”应为“地在天上”；
【校读】里面“小往大来 指阴长阳消”应为“阳长阴消”</span>
                  &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/24143286/">(<span class="">2回应</span>)</a>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-01-24 17:22</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">2人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                编辑校对还是不力啊<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>这一页就有两处错误<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>【大义】里面“天在地上”应为“地在天上”；<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>【校读】里面“小往大来 指阴长阳消”应为“阳长阴消”
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







